Magajin garin Kansas Quinton Lucas ya yi tambaya a ranar Lahadi kan dalilan Shugaba Trump na tura wakilan tarayya zuwa biranen Amurka - yana mai cewa yayin da zai yi maraba da taimakon wajen magance kashe-kashen da aka yi a garin na Midwest, yana ganin matakin zai iya zama ne game da sayen damar sake zaben Trump. .
"Na yi matukar takaici a wannan makon [cewa] shugaban ya ambaci zanga-zangar George Floyd, ya ambaci batun Black Lives Matter," Lucas, dan Democrat, ya ce a "Fox News Lahadi" na zanga-zangar kwanan nan game da bambancin launin fata da kuma zaluncin 'yan sanda.
"Wannan ba haka bane a Kansas City. Mun samu karin shekara-shekara [amma] abin da muke bukatar taimako a kansa shi ne share wasu kashe-kashen da ba a magance su ba."
