"Akwai rajistan $ 1,200 da ke zuwa. Wannan zai kasance wani ɓangare na sabon kunshin. Da na fi son a rage harajin biyan albashi, a saman wannan rajistan," Kudlow ya ce a cikin "Jihar Tarayyar."
