Ted Cruz ya ce manufar Pelosi ita ce "ba da kudi a kan matsalar sannan kuma ta rufe Amurka"
Washington - Sanatan Republican Ted Cruz daga Texas ya zargi kakakin majalisar wakilai Nancy Pelosi da House Democrats da turawa wani kunshin taimakon coronavirus wanda ya maida hankali kan "fallasa tsabar kudi a matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka" yayin da ake ci gaba da tattaunawa kan mataki na gaba.
A wata hira da ya yi da "Face the Nation" a ranar Lahadi, Cruz ya ce kasar na fuskantar rikice-rikice guda biyu a lokaci guda: wata annoba ta duniya da ta lakume rayukan mutane sama da 600,000 a duniya baki daya da kuma "cikakken bala'in tattalin arziki" a Amurka.
Amma Cruz ya ce Pelosi, wanda ya fito a "Face the Nation" a gaban sanatan, "ya mai da hankali ne kan ba wadancan ba."
"Manufofinta suna fallasa tsabar kudi a matsalar kuma sun rufe Amurka," in ji Texas Republican.
"Kuma musamman, ka kalli lissafin dala tiriliyan 3 da take kokarin tursasawa, kawai tana fallasa kudi ne ga kawayenta kuma ba za ta magance matsalar ba. Manufarmu ya kamata Amurkawa su so komawa bakin aiki. Suna son su iya samarwa ga danginsu. "
'Yan majalisar dattijan Republican da White House sun kwashe makon da ya gabata suna tattaunawa kan sharuddan kashi na hudu na maganin coronavirus, wanda suke sa ran zai ci dala tiriliyan 1.
A karshen mako, shugaban ma'aikata na fadar White House Mark Meadows da Sakataren Baitul malin Steven Mnuchin sun koma Capitol Hill don karin tattaunawa da ma'aikatan Majalisar Dattawa, kuma Mnuchin ya fada wa gidan talabijin na Fox News a wata hira da suka yi ranar Lahadi cewa Shugaban masu rinjaye na Majalisar Mitch McConnell ne zai bayyana su. ran Litinin.
Batun da ya fi daukar hankali ga ‘yan majalisar - kuma abin da ke takaddama tsakanin‘ yan jam’iyyar Republican da Democrats - shi ne karewar ingantaccen amfanin rashin aikin yi, wanda ya fara karewa a karshen makon nan.
Yayin da 'yan Democrats ke son kunshin "karo na hudu" na coronavirus don adana dala 600 ga fa'idodi,' yan Republican suna kira da a dawo da shi kuma suna jayayya cewa wasu Amurkawa sun fi samun rashin aikin yi fiye da yadda suke yi a albashi.
Cruz ya ce fiye da rabin Amurkawa da ke karɓar ingantaccen fa'idodin rashin aikin yi ana biyan su yanzu fiye da lokacin da suke aiki sannan ya ce ya yi magana da ƙananan 'yan kasuwa a Texas waɗanda ke fuskantar matsalar sake maimaita ma'aikata.
"Tabbas, ba za su dawo ba saboda gwamnatin tarayya tana biyansu, a wasu lokuta, ninki biyu na kudin da zasu zauna a gida," in ji shi.
Cruz ya ce kamata ya yi Majalisa ta mayar da hankali kan zartar da kudurin dawo da wanda zai kawo sauki ga Amurkawa su koma bakin aiki ta hanyar sassauta haraji da ka'idoji a kan kananan kamfanoni: "maimakon kawai ya cika tiriliyan daga kofa, dokar kwatowa za ta dakatar da harajin albashi, wanda zai ba shi karin albashi ga duk wanda ke Amurka wanda ke aiki. Hakan na sa mutane su koma bakin aiki, "in ji shi.
Shugaba Trump ya bukaci a makon da ya gabata shirin tallafi na gaba ya hada da rage harajin albashi, amma Mnuchin ya ce ba zai kasance cikin dokar ba, saboda shawarar ba ta da karbuwa a tsakanin ‘yan Republican.
Mista Trump ya amince da rage harajin biyan albashi ba zai kasance a kudirin doka na gaba ba amma ya nemi dora alhakin hakan a kan 'yan Democrat.
